Project: Student Management System
Description:
 Ek program banayenge jisme students ke records store, view, update aur delete kiye ja sakte hain. Ye project basic file handling aur structures ka use sikhaega.
Features:
Add a new student
Store: Name, Roll Number, Age, Marks, etc.
Display all students
List all records in a readable format.
Search a student
By Roll Number or Name.
Update student information
Modify marks, age, etc.
Delete a student record
Remove a student from the database.
Save data to a file and read it back
Data persists after program closes.
Concepts Used:
struct for student record
Arrays or linked list for storing multiple records
FILE handling (fopen, fwrite, fread)
Functions for each operation (add, display, search, update, delete)
Loops and conditional statements (for, while, if)
Optional Add-ons:
Sort students by marks or name
Calculate class average marks
Password protection for admin access
1. System Diagram (Flow)
mathematica
Start
  |
  v
[Main Menu]
  |
  |--1. Add Student ---> [Input Student Details] ---> [Save to List/File] ---> Back to Menu
  |
  |--2. Display All ---> [Read All Records from List/File] ---> [Show on Screen] ---> Back to Menu
  |
  |--3. Search Student ---> [Enter Roll Number/Name] ---> [Find in List/File] ---> [Show Details or Not Found] ---> Back to Menu
  |
  |--4. Update Student ---> [Search Record] ---> [Modify Details] ---> [Save Changes] ---> Back to Menu
  |
  |--5. Delete Student ---> [Search Record] ---> [Remove from File] ---> Back to Menu
  |
  |--6. Exit ---> End Program
2. Explanation of Each Part
Main Menu
User ko options dikhata hai: Add, Display, Search, Update, Delete, Exit.
Loop use hota hai menu pe wapas aane ke liye jab tak user exit na kare.
Add Student
User se details lete hain:
Name
Roll Number
Age
Marks
Ye details ek structure (struct) me store ki jaati hain.
Fir list ya file me save karte hain.
Display All
Stored records ko screen pe print karte hain.
Agar file use ho rahi hai, toh file se data read karte hain.
Agar array/list use ho rahi hai, toh array iterate karke print karte hain.
Search Student
User se Roll Number ya Name input lete hain.
List/file me check karte hain.
Agar record milta hai, details show karte hain, warna “Not Found” message.
Update Student
Pehle record search karte hain (Search logic reuse hota hai).
Fir user ko option dete hain fields update karne ke liye (age, marks, etc.).
Changes save karte hain list/file me.
Delete Student
Pehle record search karte hain.
Record milne par list/file se delete kar dete hain.
Agar array use hai, toh remaining records shift karne padte hain.
Exit
Program end hota hai.
Agar file use ho rahi hai, toh ensure karna ke data save ho gaya hai.
Ye system beginner ke liye perfect C language project hai kyunki:
struct aur arrays ka practice milta hai
File handling sikhi ja sakti hai
Loops aur conditions practice hoti hai
Real-world application ka feel milta hai

